  "remarks": "\nFormer Deputy Prime Minister of the Russian Federation in charge of the Defence Industry.  Publicly called for the annexation of Crimea and for the further integration of Crimea into the Russian Federation.  Since May 2018 holds the position of General Director in Roscosmos, a state corporation. \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
